    {
      "id": "501fa7a6-9175-4a24-a625-acb679fe6ef6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper uses data of student mobility between 2007 and 2016. The authors have constructed a weighted directed network that analyses how mobility changed over the years.",
